    "description": "Pet Sanctuary is a relaxing game where you take care of your cherished pets. From feeding them fruit to choosing a favorite outfit, you take care of and nature your chosen pet in this bright and joyful world. Plus, with mini games like Snake and Memory Mountain, you can earn rewards that your pet will love.<br><br><u>Play minigames to earn items and food to help train your pets.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/21d8ec19f4edaa2c73b64be2d6a04740.poster.avif?t=1721745463\" width=682 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/21d8ec19f4edaa2c73b64be2d6a04740.webm?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/21d8ec19f4edaa2c73b64be2d6a04740.mp4?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Customize your pets with different skins and items.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/edf740bafa9e0ea4d775331c4d4e3412.poster.avif?t=1721745463\" width=682 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/edf740bafa9e0ea4d775331c4d4e3412.webm?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/edf740bafa9e0ea4d775331c4d4e3412.mp4?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Hang out with and interact with your pets.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/7a7c2be51959554e925a1036f309f353.poster.avif?t=1721745463\" width=682 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/7a7c2be51959554e925a1036f309f353.webm?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/7a7c2be51959554e925a1036f309f353.mp4?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Enter your pets in races to unlock new characters, skin, and accessories for your pets</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/913f66c8128d5cf713a94a93ae4f2e66.poster.avif?t=1721745463\" width=682 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/913f66c8128d5cf713a94a93ae4f2e66.webm?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402690/extras/913f66c8128d5cf713a94a93ae4f2e66.mp4?t=1721745463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
